Yandex,is,the,largest,search,engine,in,Russia,and,develops,a,number,of,Internet,based,services,and,products,Yandex,offers,owners,of,websites,and,blogs,tools,with,which,they,can,apply,the,functional,services,of,Yandex,in,their,projects,The,site,and,documentation,are,in,Russian,The,Blog,Search,API,is,a,tool,that,lets,integrate,the,Yandex,Blog,Search,service,on,their,site,whether,it,is,a,personal,blog,forum,or,blogohosting,The,API,can,index,a,personal,blog,or,any,blogs,on,any,platform,and,perform,a,detailed,search,It,uses,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,or,RSS